00:03.462 --> 00:04.463
It's absolutely fair.

00:04.505 --> 00:06.047
I'm getting hungry.

00:06.089 --> 00:07.090
We're doing it my way.

00:07.132 --> 00:08.425
They're getting cold.

00:08.467 --> 00:10.135
You want them

00:08.467 --> 00:10.135
