00:22.397 --> 00:24.733
Dewey!

00:24.775 --> 00:26.318
Okay, we're going to assume

00:26.360 --> 00:29.070
this was a four-incher

00:26.360 --> 00:29.070
from the share pile.

00:29.112 --> 00:30.155
117 minus three,

00:30.197 --> 00:33.074
times 29, divided by three,

00:30.197 --> 00:33.074
